column5: Well this rainy weather is going to keep us off the Main River after 3 days of ice fishing ...I will keep ya up to date on ice but it might be a week or so before we get back out ...lets hope this warm front dont make the ice go out everthing was looking good .
It's too bad. Just when everything was looking so promising everywhere for a great early season start!
I think we'll be starting from scratch again waiting for fresh ice... 3 days of 10 degrees but worst part is the forecasted 10mm of rain all three days.
